<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="EUC-KR">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>아싸컴</title>
</head>
<style>
	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
	a { color: #000; }

	.error_container { height: 440px; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }

	.error_container .error_imgBox { width: 880px; height: 440px;  }

	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_leftImg { width: 340px; height: 440px; float: left;  }

	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox { width: 487px; height: 255px; padding: 106px 33px 0 20px; float: right; }
	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .text_title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: "notokr M", sans-serif; }
	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .text_title:after { content: ""; display: block; width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid #000; margin-top: 5px; }

	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .text_content { font-family: "notokr M", sans-serif; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 14px; }

	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_logoBox { width: 487px; height: 56px; position: relative; float: right; padding: 0 33px 0 0; }
	.error_container .error_imgBox .error_logoBox img { position: absolute; top: 0; right: 33px; }

	@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
		.error_container { height: auto; }
		.error_container .error_imgBox { width: 375px; height: 600px;  }

		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_leftImg { width: 300px; height: 300px; position: absolute; top: 20%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); position: relative; }
		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_leftImg img { width: 300px; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }

		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox { width: 280px; height:200px; padding: 50px 33px; position: absolute; top: 67%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .text_title { font-size: 22px; }
		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .text_content { font-size: 14px; }
		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_textBox .center { text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }

		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_logoBox { position: absolute; top: 96%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
		.error_container .error_imgBox .error_logoBox img { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
	}
</style>
<body>
	<div class="error_container">
		<div class="error_imgBox">
			<div class="error_leftImg">
				<img src="/shop/images/index_errorimg_new.jpg" alt="접근차단이미지">
			</div>
			<div class="error_textBox">
				<p class="text_title">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</p>
				<p class="text_content">
					페이지의 주소가 변경 혹은 삭제되어 요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.<br><br>
					입력하신 주소가 정확한지 다시 한번 확인해 주시기 바랍니다.<br><br>
				</p>
				<p class="center"><a href="/">[아싸컴 홈으로]</a></p>
			</div>
			<div class="error_logoBox">
				<img src="/shop/main/images2/assacom_logo.jpg" alt="로고이미지">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>